name: SILICONE WRISTBANDS
description:
100% Silicone Wristband. Eight inch circumference. Fits men and women comfortably. Mix and match!

This is a modern day "WWJD" to serve as a reminder for you as you spend your money. 

Your money makes a statement. What has yours been saying???


Support the Movement.
Support Black Businesses.

(click photo for larger image)

**price includes domestic shipping**

description:

color: RED. BLACK. GREEN 

Hanes Mens Tees.

OUR TWO CENTS:
